# cpu
${font Poky:size=20}P${voffset -3}${font Impact:size=16}$color1${goto 30}${cpu cpu0}${goto 55}${color}%${color1}${goto 80}${font}${voffset -10}${top name 1}${goto 150}${top cpu 1}$color
